1
00:00:02,880 --> 00:00:03,880
What is it?

2
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,040
For me...

3
00:00:27,210 --> 00:00:30,000
Makishima Reika,
a senior one year older than me.

4
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,000
Reika-senpai.

5
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:32,630
Good morning.

6
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:33,290
Morning.

7
00:00:33,460 --> 00:00:35,580
She was totally out of my league.

8
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:39,000
Reika-senpai was absolutely perfect.

9
00:00:39,630 --> 00:00:42,460
She was the student council president
and worked as a model.

10
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:45,130
She got great grades
and was a natural at sports.

11
00:00:45,630 --> 00:00:48,830
Lively and cheerful,
strong and graceful.

12
00:00:50,830 --> 00:00:51,960
And on top of all that...

13
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:09,250
What are you doing?
